sourcesContent:
let timelineElements = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Frontend Developer",
    location: "Rosario, Argentina",
    description:
      "Starting my journey in development universe. Compiling courses from Microsoft Learn, UDEMY, MDN Web Docs and building projects. I've learned to build React Apps, WebSite and more.",
    date: "May 2022 - Infinity and Beyond",
    icon: "school",
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Pack OFFICE Specialist",
    location: "Rosario, Argentina",
    description:
      "Working hand-in-hand with small businesses, entrepreneur and micro business. Building Excel Sheets for accounting / stock managements / clients data bases. Building PowerPoint presentations for medical keynotes or political congresses",
    date: "June 2013 - August 2016",
    icon: "work",
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "Move from France to Argentina",
    location: "Rosario, Argentina",
    description:
      "In december 2020 i moved to Argentina. As an adaptable, active listener person, In few months I learned spanish and the Argentinian culture.",
    date: "December 2020",
    icon: "school",
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    title: "Producer Morning News Show",
    location: "Paris, France",
    description:
      "I had the chance to produce the morning news show of RFI radio, working with the bests journalists of France. I also produced and edited radio-documentaries and radio-fictions.",
    date: "August 2018 - September 2020",
    icon: "work",
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    title: "Producer / Director Entertainement ",
    location: "Paris, France",
    description:
      "At my 19 years old I moved to Paris and went to a radio school, I had my diploma in 2012 then, I started at the bottom of the chain and grow to Artistic Director of a Tv Show in 'NRJ 12'. I was the youngest producer in a national radio when I started in 2013 at 'Virgin Radio France' With those years I've learned to managed teams, to analyse ratings and to understand and apply the client needs",
    date: "2013 - 2018",
    icon: "work",
  },
  {
    id: 6,
    title: "Marketing and Economy diploma",
    location: "Nice, France",
    description:
      "Highschool .",
    date: "2003 - 2007",
    icon: "school",
  },
];

export default timelineElements;
